2. Dibernardo A, Cote T, Ogden NH, Lindsay LR. The prevalence of _Borrelia miyamotoi_ infection, and other co-infections with other _Borrelia_ spp in _Ixodes scapularis_ tick collected in Canada. Parasit Vectors 2014; 7: 183; https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4001108/
3. Krakowetz CN, Dibernardo A, Lindsay LR, Chilton NB. Two _Anaplasma phagocytophilum_ strains in _Ixodes scapularis_ ticks, Canada. Emerg Infect Dis. 2014; 20(12): 2064-67; https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4257797/

